snippet.title: Our Last Stand - a Way Home Official Teaser
snippet.description:
Our Last Stand - a Way Home is a Survival Horror l Zombie  Game taking place in Nusantara that will focus on Stealth or Action depending on how the Player play the Game.

Synopsis :
Habib Pines is a lone wolf survivor of Last Stand surviving community, he usually doing his mission all alone until he realized he didn;t need to do everything by himself anymore.
